  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT SKEL DUNGEON HERE!</h1><p></p><br><h1>YOU MIGHT ALSO LIKE</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This is a place for those who gather to receive a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity in the structure of time. Members sometimes become friends, and sometimes turn out to be enemies in order to finish their own assignment. <br>Kirel, our amnesiac protagonist who has forgotten even his own name is put on a test.<br>Everything depends on your choice.<br>You only have 7 days! <br>And what would be your choice?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>features</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494140/extras/6d015298feffab05bebed14383a9f68e.poster.avif?t=1729549485\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494140/extras/6d015298feffab05bebed14383a9f68e.webm?t=1729549485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494140/extras/6d015298feffab05bebed14383a9f68e.mp4?t=1729549485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- Casual gameplay in instant messaging format<br>- Mystery text adventure<br>- Your choice impact the story and relationships between characters<br>- Every character has their own secret and story<br>- A lot of challenges and collectibles<br>- A multi-episode story with branching paths that leads to four different endings<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Everything depends on your choices.</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494140/extras/7a6f200a2dc1c4276e915352fbcf974d.poster.avif?t=1729549485\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1494140/extras/7a6f200a2dc1c4276e91